Terrayne Crawford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terrayne_Crawford 0 Terrayne Crawford (sometimes credited as Terry Crawford born February 13, 1945) is an American actress known for her role as Beth Chavez and Edith Collins on the popular ABC-TV soap opera Dark Shadows from 1968 to 1971.
